  "PinObjectiveTip": {
    "English": "<span class=\"name name-special\">Hadal Cores</span> are found around <span class=\"name name-commodity\">alluring plant specimens</span> on the sea bed. Use the Galaxy Map to locate systems with ocean planets.<br><span class=\"name name-fuel\">CAUTION</span>: Hadal cores attract biological anomalies.<br>While swimming, identify <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Alluring Specimens</span> with the <span class=\"name name-technology\">Analysis Visor</span>.<br>Increase marine efficiency by upgrading the Exosuit <span class=\"name name-technology\">Aeration Membrane</span>, refilling oxygen supplies from <span class=\"name name-tradeable\">Kelp Sacs</span>, or travelling in a <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Nautilon Submarine</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "<span class=\"name name-special\">超深渊核心</span>常见于海床上<span class=\"name name-commodity\">诱人的植物样本</span>附近。使用星系图定位有海洋行星的恒星系。<br><span class=\"name name-fuel\">警告</span>：超深渊核心会吸引生物异象。<br>游泳时，用<span class=\"name name-technology\">分析面甲</span>识别<span class=\"name name-stellar\">诱人样本</span>。<br>升级套装的<span class=\"name name-technology\">曝气膜</span>，从<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">海藻袋</span>中补充氧气补给，或搭乘<span class=\"name name-stellar\">大鹦鹉螺潜水艇</span>出行，以提高在海洋中的效率。",
    "TencentChinese": "<span class=\"name name-special\">超深渊核心</span>常见于海床上的<span class=\"name name-commodity\">诱人的植物样本</span>附近。使用星系图定位有海洋行星的恒星系。<br><span class=\"name name-fuel\">警告</span>：超深渊核心会吸引生物异象。<br>游泳时，用<span class=\"name name-technology\">分析面甲</span>识别<span class=\"name name-stellar\">诱人样本</span>。<br>升级套装的<span class=\"name name-technology\">曝气膜</span>，从<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">海藻袋</span>中补充氧气补给，或搭乘<span class=\"name name-stellar\">大鹦鹉螺潜水艇</span>出行，以提高在海洋中的效率。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "<span class=\"name name-special\">海溝核心</span>可於海底的<span class=\"name name-commodity\">誘人植物樣本</span>附近找到。利用銀河系地圖尋找含有海洋星球的星系。<br><span class=\"name name-fuel\">注意</span>：海溝核心會吸引生物異常。<br>游泳時，利用<span class=\"name name-technology\">分析護目鏡</span>來偵測<span class=\"name name-stellar\">誘人植物樣本</span>。<br>升級強化套裝的<span class=\"name name-technology\">曝氣黏膜</span>、從<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">巨藻囊</span>補充氧氣補給，或搭乘<span class=\"name name-stellar\">巡洋龍潛艇</span>前進，以提高海洋行動的效率。"
  },
